metadata.name: "The Keeper Of The White Raptor"
metadata.description:
The Prologue: 

The Keeper of the White Raptor was a mysterious figure known throughout the land for his exceptional hunting skills and his ability to tame the wildest of beasts. He was a solitary man, rarely seen in the company of others, and it was said that he possessed a deep connection with the creatures of the forest. Many sought his counsel and paid handsomely for his services, but The Keeper was selective about his clients, choosing only those who he believed were worthy of his time and expertise. Despite his reputation, few knew his true identity or the secrets he held close to his heart. But one thing was certain - The Keeper was a force to be reckoned with, and those who crossed him did so at their own peril.
